                                    <input type="hidden" id="overview-about-text" value="%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMulti-Antioxidant%20Radiance%20Serum&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3Eis%20a%20daily%20serum%20combining%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20antioxidant%20and%20protective%20technologies%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Ecombat%20multiple%20concerns%20associated%20with%20environmental%20damage%3C/strong%3E%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Evisibly%20brighten%20dull%20skin%3C/strong%3E.&amp;nbsp;%3C/p%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3EMulti-Active%20Radiance%20Serum%20works%20to%20combat%20environmental%20stressors,%20like%20pollution%20and%20smog,%20which%20can%20make%20skin%20look%20dull%20and%20prematurely%20aged.%20The%20formulation%20%3Cstrong%3Eboosts%20radiance%3C/strong%3E,%20while%20helping%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Efade%20visible%20dark%20spots%3C/strong%3E%20an%3Cstrong%3Ed%20smooth%20the%20look%20of%20skin%20texture%3C/strong%3E,%20all%20of%20which%20help%20to%20reduce%20the%20appearance%20of%20atmospheric%20skin%20aging.&amp;nbsp;%3C/p%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3EMulti-Antioxidant%20Radiance%20Serum%20combines%20a%20total%20of%208%20technologies,%20including%20vitamin%20C%20and%20ginseng,%20and%20achieves%20a%20multi-faceted%20approach%20to%20antioxidant%20protection%20suited%20to%20use%20both%20in%20the%20day%20and%20at%20night.%20When%20used%20in%20the%20day,%20the%20serum-textured%20formulation%20helps%20shield%20against%20the%20damaging%20effects%20of%20pollution,%20while%20providing%20barrier%20strengthening%20and%20lasting%20hydration%20for%20enhanced%20skin%20resilience.&amp;nbsp;%3C/p%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3EWhen%20used%20at%20night,%20it%20continues%20to%20offer%20antioxidant%20protection%20while%20skin%20is%20in%20its%20resting%20and%20repair%20stages,%20working%20to%20boost%20radiance%20for%20skin%20that%20is%20visibly%20more%20radiant%20during%20the%20day.%3C/p%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20our%20range%20of%20%3Ca%20href=%22theordinary-multi-active%22%3EMulti-Active%20Solutions%3C/a%3E,%20the%208%20key%20technologies%20found%20in%20Multi-Antioxidant%20Radiance%20Serum%20are:%3C/p%3E%0D%0A%0D%0A%3Cul%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAscorbyl%20Glucoside:&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3EA%20stabilized%20form%20of%20vitamin%20C,%20which%20is%20converted%20to%20its%20active%20form%20inside%20the%20skin.%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGinseng%20Extract:&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3EA%20plant%20extract%20that%20helps%20protect%20and%20soothethe&amp;nbsp;%20skin&amp;rsquo;s%20stress%20response%20against%20environmental%20aggressors.%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEGCG:&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3EDesigned%20to%20help%20shield%20against%20environmental%20irritants,%20while%20protecting%20skin%20from%20external%20stressors%20that%20can%20contribute%20to%20signs%20of%20aging.&amp;nbsp;%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcetyl%20Tetrapeptide-2%3C/strong%3E:%20A%20protective%20biomimetic%20peptide%20which%20helps%20target%20the%20appearance%20of%20uneven%20skin%20tone%20to%20promote%20a%20more%20radiant,%20healthier-looking%20appearance.&amp;nbsp;%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeptapeptide-6:&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3EA%20turmeric%20peptide%20that%20helps%20protect%20against%20environmental%20aggressors%20while%20also%20targeting%20common%20signs%20of%20aging.%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EErgothioneine:&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3EAn%20antioxidant%20found%20naturally%20within%20the%20skin,%20that%20helps%20provide%20protection%20against%20environmental%20stressors,%20which%20can%20cause%20visible%20skin%20damage.&amp;nbsp;%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETocotrienols:&amp;nbsp;%3C/strong%3EDerived%20from%20annatto%20seeds%20and%20a%20source%20of%20Vitamin%20E,%20these%20molecules%20help%20protect%20from%20the%20damaging%20effects%20of%20environmental%20pollution%20that%20can%20contribute%20to%20signs%20of%20atmospheric%20skin%20aging,%20while%20soothing%20signs%20of%20skin%20irritation%20that%20can%20be%20caused%20by%20environmental%20stressors.%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETremella%20Fuciformis%20Sporocarp%20Extract%3C/strong%3E:%20A%20polysaccharide%20(chain%20of%20sugar-like%20molecules)%20derived%20from%20snow%20fungus,%20which%20creates%20a%20protective%20film%20on%20the%20skin&amp;rsquo;s%20surface,%20helping%20to%20attract%20and%20hold%20on%20to%20water%20like%20a%20moisture%20magnet.&amp;nbsp;%3C/li%3E%0D%0A%3C/ul%3E">
